# Monorepo — Nextgen CMS

مرجع کلی: `AGENTS.md`

## Workspaces

- Root: `nextgen-cms` — `npm workspaces`
- Deploy app: `@nextgen-cms/pelak` در `apps/pelak` (تنها app)
- Packages: `@nextgen-cms/contract|core|config|site-data|studio|seed`
- `packages/studio` package منطق admin است — app حذف‌شدهٔ `apps/studio` نیست

## وابستگی مجاز

```
contract (leaf)
core ← contract
config ← core + contract
site-data ← core + config + contract
studio ← core + config + contract
seed ← core
apps/pelak ← all
```

## Import

- کد جدید: `@nextgen-cms/*` — نه `@/lib/*` (shim منسوخ)
- کامپوننت‌های app: `@/components/*` داخل `apps/pelak`

## Build

```bash
npm run dev
npm run build        # بدون migrate/seed
```

## تغییر schema

1. `packages/core/src/db/schema/`
2. `npm run db:generate -w @nextgen-cms/core`
3. commit migration در `packages/core/drizzle/`

جزئیات: `docs/MIGRATION-POLICY.md`
